### The rise of the web has taken JavaScript places it was never conceived to be. It has become one of the most important languages in today’s world. In our previous JavaScript Tutorial, we discussed all the basics and fundamentals of the language. In this Advanced JavaScript Tutorial, we will learn about some of the advanced aspects of the programming language in the following sequence:

